<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_76855742-a989-450c-a2ce-0cfa06ffeb90" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="NSW"><sptc>B2D6</sptc><title id="_91053e26-8911-4693-becb-5ab1ce46a53c">Temperature control devices</title><archive-num>2019: NSW B2.6(2)(d), Application 1 and Exemption 1</archive-num><subclause id="_b42844b8-905e-4977-a1bd-4ac0fa96a374" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_094f959a-6117-4169-94ce-eebee6a53000">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A temperature control device used to deliver <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1334_0.4.0.xml#_92b3a3dc-59e4-425f-909b-d8eb03e6460a" id="_df0c31a3-d521-44de-bce6-4a047895d562" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">heated water</xref> in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1655_1.28.0.xml#_c59b9c99-8790-4a71-8a7e-4952cd7b212b" id="_a15a95af-08e8-40c1-bba7-b95b50c38da9" scope="local" type="subclause">B2D5(a)</xref> must be a—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_ba2f741d-87ef-4f1b-b9b1-c6424c524edd">thermostatic mixing valve; or</li><li id="_f10ae29b-97ea-4a44-8429-3410ecd6c2cd">thermostatically controlled tap.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_052f1f6d-ed5c-4109-a718-893ca3164af4" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_8d13035f-0b17-4084-b76b-ab181bfd2e47">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>A temperature control device used to deliver <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1334_0.4.0.xml#_92b3a3dc-59e4-425f-909b-d8eb03e6460a" id="_99b0976e-6a7e-4bbf-b9e3-0105eaa23441" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">heated water</xref> in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1655_1.28.0.xml#_c59b9c99-8790-4a71-8a7e-4952cd7b212b" id="_bceb7cfb-e1b1-4e85-9ec0-bdeff7d9c879" scope="local" type="subclause">B2D5(b)</xref> must be a—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_a78a8e50-f843-4e88-b39c-42fe2d8e9462">thermostatic mixing valve; or</li><li id="_cbd8cb9a-388e-4c6e-a7ed-5e385035bd79">thermostatically controlled tap; or</li><li id="_585ba4ba-d900-4e84-958b-5b899b994b54">tempering valve; or</li><li id="_adebbac5-7a23-42d8-90e3-32a55421ec19">temperature limited water heater with a maximum delivery temperature of 50°C marked in accordance with AS 3498.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_c715da87-c380-45ac-a982-0b684633698f" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_d2360b2a-f836-46a4-8174-daad589bb5e4">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>The <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_172eb37a-6279-4b65-b6bb-40a4fc1e6796" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> maximum delivery temperature must be achieved in accordance with AS/NZS 3500.4.</p></subclause><callout id="_a42945f4-4ad8-4083-bd54-a399bc138882"><callout-type ncc-info-type="application"/><p>B2D6 only applies to sanitary fixtures for personal hygiene purposes—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_a217285d-84cb-4451-8cfb-e0d82e79f1a1">When installing new <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1334_0.4.0.xml#_92b3a3dc-59e4-425f-909b-d8eb03e6460a" id="_76174f9d-6556-47a0-9612-da29e352c24e" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">heated water</xref> services, including extensions or additions to an existing heated water service; or</li><li id="_b4a0884f-c029-41cb-87a1-dbd47186e087">When replacing a hot water heater, regardless of the type or location of the heater.</li></ol></callout><callout id="_482c2f90-13dc-4ef5-9b74-7e42dbb155cc"><callout-type ncc-info-type="exemption"/><p>A temperature control device need not be installed if one or more, but not all water heaters in a bank of water heaters are replaced.</p></callout></clause>